On a month-on-month basis, price growth was at 0.3% in January, the same rate as in the previous month. Core inflation, which excludes prices of food, non-alcoholic beverages, petrol and energy, fell to 3.7% year on year in January compared with a rate of 3.8% in December. On a month-on-month basis core inflation increased 0.1%, from 0.2% in the prior month. --Reuters--